                        <join result="defendantPunishment" targOrder="Y" targets="def1-555-18490129 t18490129-555-punishment-118"></join>Confined Eighteen Months</rs>.</hi>
               </p>
               <p>
                  <hi rend="largeCaps">PERKINS</hi>—<hi rend="smallCaps">
                     <rs id="t18490129-555-verdict-2" type="verdictDescription">
